      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S-generation RX-7 is a mechanical masterpiece in showroom condition. The 13B-REW rotary engine features exceptional compression across all rotor faces, feeding into the original sequential twin-turbocharger system with zero boost leaks. The chassis retains its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension geometry, providing telepathic handling through the corners. Power is delivered via a crisp 5-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential. Every vacuum line, cooling component, and apex seal has been meticulously maintained to ensure peak thermal efficiency and structural integrity. This is a rare, unmolested example with zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a factory-fresh interior.",
