      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this collector-grade gem. This vehicle is in truly impeccable condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and pampered in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, showroom-quality luster with absolutely no stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains factory-fresh; the premium leather is supple without a single crease, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the seat heaters, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of documented service records from authorized specialists. With zero leaks, a smooth-shifting transmission, and a perfectly responsive engine, this car drives exactly as it did when it first left the assembly line. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than the absolute best, this is an unparalleled find.",
